signature: void renderHtml(OlTag, OlTag, OlTag, OlTag, OutputStreamWriter)

enhanced_by.reason: The render method initializes the diff object required by renderHtml.
Both methods handle IOExceptions and manage OutputStreamWriter operations.
ol_newEndpoint constructs an OlTag similar to what renderHtml uses for rendering new endpoints.
ol_missingEndpoint constructs an OlTag similar to what renderHtml uses for rendering missing endpoints.
ol_deprecatedEndpoint constructs an OlTag similar to what renderHtml uses for rendering deprecated endpoints.
ol_changed constructs an OlTag similar to what renderHtml uses for rendering changed operations.
